description:
We all need an exorcism right now. An exorcism from the hollywood illusions, the lies, the absolute BS they have shoved down our throats since birth.  EVERYONE IS LYING. EVERYTHING IS A HOAX. 
The footage from this video was taken at local churches in my area and the cemetery that some of my ancestors are buried in. My ancestors came to Canada in the early 1700's to escape the European ""witch hunts"" of the Rh- bloodline. Follow the clues to find out who the real ""nazis"" are. 
Thank God for my ancestors who kept impeccable records of their journey and found a paradise here to hide future generations in and keep us alive. 
Many of you don't know that you come from these same strong people. 
Many of you don't know how extraordinarily powerful these people were and the hidden powers that you also have, which can be re-activated. 
PEACE, LOVE AND PROSPERITY! 
Be fearless! 
HUMANITY WILL WIN! 
Kaleigh 💛
